Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}How long will I be able to keep up the act?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Will I be able to say good-bye when you want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}The signs I'd missed that day fade bit by bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}But I'm sure things will be fine - we'll meet again, just as we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Is it too late to leave a few small wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Will I be able to say "welcome back" when the light has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}I must go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Call that the most beautiful thing in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Just wait until we take back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}all that's been stolen from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}More
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Round and round, make me dizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Back and forth, sway me like never before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Brighter and brighter, let it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Softly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}I summon forth the wounded night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}And cast a single little magic spell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}And just like that, we can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Don't avert your gaze! Keep it straight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Nothing will stop us at this point
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Until the magic wears off - until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Hold on tight! To my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}My hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Not a single one left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}We'll reclaim every last piece, that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Until the magic wears off - until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}Hold on tight! To my hand, my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.4}My hand!
